common_filenames.filename: chatall-history-[YYYYMMDD]-[hours, minutes, and seconds since midnight].ChatALL
common_filenames.description: chatall-history-[YYYYMMDD]-[hours, minutes, and seconds since midnight].ChatALL - Naming convention ChatALL uses to name CHATALL files when exporting them. For example, exporting a CHATALL file on February 12, 2024, at 3:46 (and 12 seconds) pm results in the following filename: chatall-history-20240212-154612.ChatALL .
